user.about:
Hey there! My name is Meredith and I am a 26 year old Dental Hygienist here in WA. My two favorite things in life are coffee and shopping. I am a MAJOR impulse buyer, lucky for you they all end up on Vinted!. 
I assure you that I take very good care of my clothing. I pay very close attention to the washing directions on tags. If it says hand wash, then it has been hand washed. All other clothing is washed inside out and usually on a delicate cycle to keep them looking new. They also come from a smoke-free home, we do have a dog but I assure you I do not him jump on me in my beautiful clothes! Everything is washed before being sent, unless it is brand new with tags of course. I am a quality seller I promise!
If you have any questions please do not hesitate to ask them! I always ship out as soon as possible. I am willing to bundle and negotiate prices, but please be reasonable.
Happy Vinting!
